1
00:00:08,517 --> 00:00:10,042
Simon, how long have you lived in Boston?
Simon, 你在波士顿住多久了?

2
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:12,745
Two and a half years.
两年半了.

3
00:00:13,756 --> 00:00:14,566
Are you enjoying it?
你喜欢这儿吗?

4
00:00:15,025 --> 00:00:15,413
Absolutely.
当然.

5
00:00:16,411 --> 00:00:20,021
Boston's so small and charming and manageable after London.
我觉得波士顿小而迷人, 能应付的.在伦敦住过以后,

6
00:00:20,449 --> 00:00:23,689
It's a big city to me, after growing up in Bunkie, Louisiana.
这里对我来说是个大城市.在我在路易斯安那州的邦基市(Bunkie,Louisiana)长大后

7
00:00:24,366 --> 00:00:26,767
I love the museums here, and art galleries.
我喜爱这里的博物馆, 和艺术馆.

8
00:00:27,456 --> 00:00:28,488
And the beautiful stores.
还有美丽的商店.

9
00:00:29,202 --> 00:00:29,747
And restaurants.
还有饭店.

10
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:33,049
Well, you can't get my momma's hot cakes in Boston.
Well, 你吃不到我妈妈做的热点心 在波士顿.

11
00:00:33,521 --> 00:00:36,613
Ah, but Boston baked beans and lobster...
Ah, 但波士顿有烤青豆和龙虾...

12
00:00:36,938 --> 00:00:37,290
Right.
那倒也是.

13
00:00:37,809 --> 00:00:40,821
Isn't it a bit strange for you, living in Yankee country?
不会有点奇怪吗,对你来说, 住在洋基队的城市?

14
00:00:41,258 --> 00:00:41,670
Maybe a little.
也许有一点儿.

15
00:00:42,426 --> 00:00:44,090
No stranger than your situation.
不会比你的情况更奇怪.

16
00:00:44,569 --> 00:00:45,916
You didn't win either, remember?
你们也没赢, 记得吗?

17
00:00:46,484 --> 00:00:46,719
True.
是的.

18
00:00:48,661 --> 00:00:50,999
Have you noticed that Boston drivers are quite mad?
你注意到没有, 波士顿的司机们开车很疯狂?

19
00:00:51,282 --> 00:00:53,432
Oh I have. But I can live with that.
Oh I have. 但我还受得了.

20
00:00:54,002 --> 00:00:55,400
Do you know what I really don't like?
你知道我真正不喜欢的是什么吗?

21
00:00:55,771 --> 00:00:56,071
What?
什么?

22
00:00:56,451 --> 00:00:57,318
The freezing winters.
冻死人的冬天.

23
00:00:57,938 --> 00:00:58,327
Ah.
Ah.

24
00:00:58,736 --> 00:01:00,960
And they're forever going outside in the cold.
而天这么冷他们也总是外出.

25
00:01:01,659 --> 00:01:03,026
Hardy New Englanders, Sharon.
耐冻的新西兰人啊, Sharon.

26
00:01:03,585 --> 00:01:04,592
You'll have to get used to it.
你不得不习惯这些的.

